# Auto-Deploy to Vercel (sakura-erp-system-miuq)

## CRITICAL: Post-Operation Workflow

**Jab bhi koi prompt/operation pura ho jaye**, automatically ye steps follow karo:

1. **Commit & Push**: `.\sync-to-git.ps1` chalao (agar koi changes hon)
2. **Deploy**: `.\deploy-vercel-cli.ps1` chalao
3. **User ko batao**: "Deployment complete. Live: https://sakura-erp-system-miuq.vercel.app/"

## Commands (run from repo root)

```powershell
.\sync-to-git.ps1
.\deploy-vercel-cli.ps1
```

## Deployment Target

- **URL**: https://sakura-erp-system-miuq.vercel.app/
- **Method**: Vercel CLI (`vercel --prod`) from frontend folder
- **Source**: `ERP_Final - - Without_React2\ERP_Final - - Without_React\sakura-erp-migration\frontend`

## Notes

- sync-to-git.ps1: Adds all, commits, pushes to origin main
- deploy-vercel-cli.ps1: CDs to frontend, runs `npx vercel --prod --yes`
- Agar sync me "No changes" aaye, phir bhi deploy chalao (latest code ensure karega)
